# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Zuzu nest .gitignore
#
# Philosophy: this repo should contain everything needed to RECREATE the
# nest on a fresh machine, and NOTHING else. No targets, no loot, no
# personal OSINT, no pcaps, no memory, no creds, no session state.
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Secrets & credentials ──────────────────────────────────────────
*.key
*.pem
*.crt
*.pfx
*.p12
*.env
.env*
secrets/
tokens/
credentials/
.netrc
.aws/
.ssh/
authorized_keys
known_hosts
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
id_ecdsa*
id_dsa*
*.gpg
*.asc

# ── Browser/session/cookie data ────────────────────────────────────
.browser/
sessions/
cookies/
cookies.txt
*.session
*-session.json

# ── Logs, caches, temp ─────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
cache/
.cache/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
node_modules/
.venv/
.venv-*/
tmp/
*.tmp
*.swp
*~
*.restore
*.bak
*.orig

# ── OS / IDE noise ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml

# ── OpenClaw / ClawHub internal state ──────────────────────────────
.openclaw/
.clawhub/

# ── Memory: personal session log + conversation traces ─────────────
# These belong on the local machine only. Each Zuzu instance builds
# its own memory; cloning the repo should NOT inherit conversations.
MEMORY.md
memory/
memory/.dreams/

# ── Orchestrator runtime state ─────────────────────────────────────
# state/ holds live engagement state (which target, which phase, what's
# already been tried). It's runtime data, not config.
state/

# ── Reports — local only ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Every report is target-specific and may contain creds, hashes, flags,
# pcaps, screenshots, scan output, BloodHound dumps, etc. It is NEVER
# safe to commit a report unredacted. Keep them local.
#
# Exception: templates/ (committed) and any *redacted* lessons we
# explicitly move to learnings/ live outside reports/.
reports/
loot/

# ── Network captures & binary artefacts ────────────────────────────
*.pcap
*.pcapng
*.cap
*.gnmap
*.nmap
*.xml
*.hccapx
*.hccap
*.22000

# Windows / .NET / Kerberos artefacts
*.exe
*.dll
*.msi
*.iso
*.bin
*.ccache
*.kirbi
*.ntds
*.dit

# Common loot extensions
*.zip
*.7z
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.rar

# Common BloodHound output
*_users.json
*_groups.json
*_computers.json
*_domains.json
*_gpos.json
*_ous.json
*_containers.json
bloodhound_*

# ── Skill runtime output ───────────────────────────────────────────
skills/**/result.txt
skills/**/output.txt
skills/**/scratch/

# ── Wordlists (large, available from system) ──────────────────────
rockyou*.txt
top1000*.txt
*-passwords.txt
*-users.txt

# ── Git/dev junk ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git/maintenance.lock
